<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.840370>
    dc:description "FIGURES 40 – 43. Dorsal view of habitus and aedeagi of Melanterius tasmaniensis (Lea) and M. porcatus Erichson. 40 – 41: M. tasmaniensis; 40: male (New South Wales, Vincentia); 41: aedeagus (A. C. T., Tidbinbilla Road). 42 – 43: M. porcatus; 42: male (Tasmania, Bathurst Harbour); 43: adeagus (Tasmania, Hobart)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/840370/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

